remove

public AjaxOutput remove(java.lang.String listProperty,
                         int indexToDelete,
                         java.lang.String displayName)
Deletes an element in a list property of the current session command, shifting everything else around as appropriate.

Note that other than the extract command bit, this is entirely non-ae-flow-specific.

Returns:
A list of changes indicating which elements of the list were moved and where to. This list will be empty if the requested change is invalid or if the change is a no-op. The element to remove will be represented by a move to a negative index.
